data.title: 准备以至少20秒的时间回答以下问题
data.answer: I have warm, loving parents, who, despite conflicts that we had over the years, have imprinted in me a kind of belief that I can rely on their support if I need it. When I have a problem or a challenge, I can always talk to them. Listening can be hard. What I appreciate the most about them is that they're great listeners. I feel like I can tell them anything and that they truly hear me, lovingly and non-judgmentally. They pay closer attention to moments when I seemed genuinely overwhelmed by difficulties and give me a hand in overcoming them. (101字)
data.referenceText: Who are some people you can depend on when you need help? What makes them dependable?
data.referenceTranslate: 当你需要帮助时，你可以依靠谁?是什么让他们可靠?
